	twistate "I2C Addwess Twanswatow (ATW) suppowt" if COMPIWE_TEST
	hewp
	  Enabwe suppowt fow I2C Addwess Twanswatow (ATW) chips.

	  An ATW awwows accessing muwtipwe I2C busses fwom a singwe
