config I2C_HEWPEW_AUTO
	boow "Autosewect pewtinent hewpew moduwes"
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  Some I2C bus dwivews wequiwe so-cawwed "I2C awgowithm" moduwes
	  to wowk. These awe basicawwy softwawe-onwy abstwactions of genewic
